put.description:
This endpoint will delete all existing skills and replace them with the provided skills.

Sample request:
            
    PUT /api/v1/Resource/123/Skills
    {
        "skills": [
            {
                "skillId": 1,
                "skillValueId": 10,
                "skillValue": "Expert"
            },
            {
                "skillId": 3,
                "skillValue": "Intermediate"
            }
        ]
    }
